flowchart TB
    U[User: Sarthi] --> M[main agent\nOrchestrator]
    M --> MOD[moderator\nprogress + watchdog]
    M --> O[outline-first planner]

    O --> R[research agent]
    O --> C[coder agent]
    O --> T[tx agent]
    O --> J[janitor agent]

    MOD --> SW[swarm coordinator\n(task states)]
    SW --> WR[worker-research-*\n(ephemeral)]
    SW --> WC[worker-code-*\n(ephemeral)]
    SW --> WV[worker-verify-*\n(ephemeral)]

    subgraph SANDBOX[Sandbox Domains]
      R --> SR[(session sandbox)]
      C --> SC[(session sandbox)]
      T --> ST[(agent sandbox)]
      WR --> S1[(ephemeral sandbox)]
      WC --> S2[(ephemeral sandbox)]
      WV --> S3[(ephemeral sandbox)]
    end

    J --> HOST[Host monitoring/cleanup\n(sandbox off)]
    MOD --> HOST

    M --> SM[State machine\nCREATED/CLAIMED/RUNNING/DONE/FAILED/RETRYING]
    M --> AJ[JSONL audit logs + rotation]

    SR --> EXT[External APIs]
    SC --> REPO[Repos/toolchains]
    ST --> PAY[Payment rails]
